Business Setup

Partnership Firm Registration

Partnership firm registration in India is provided as per the Partnership Act, 1932. Partnership firms are registered with the registrar of firms of your respective state.

Business Setup

PAN Application

PAN enables the department to identify/ link all transactions of the PAN holder with the department. It also be used to file Income Tax Returns

Business Setup

Company Registration

Incorporating a Company under Companies Act 2013 will have many financial and legal advantages in an organization in corporate form. Organizing a business in corporate form allows a company to function independently from the owners of the business as it is treated as separate legal entity.

Business Setup

TDS Registration

TDS Return is a quarterly statement submitted by the deductor to the Income Tax Department. The statement shows a summary of all the entries for TDS collected by the deductor and the TDS paid by the deductor to the Income Tax Authority.
